              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Large sodium-iodide crystal in association",
                "with an anticoincidence plastic scintillator shell was",
                "used. This spectrometer consists of a NaI(Tl)",
                "cylinder (d=23.8 cm, height=35.6 cm) viewed by seven",
                "RCA4900 photomultiplier (PMTs), an annulus of plastic",
                "scintillator (BC408) (inner d=28.86 cm, thickness=9.84",
                "cm, length=61 cm) divided into six optically separated",
                "sectors each viewed by two Amperex XP-2202 PMTs and a",
                "front disc (d=48.58 cm, thickness=8 cm) viewed by three",
                "XP-2202 PMTs mounted on side of the disc and spaced",
                "120 degr. apart."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Targets with the thicknesses between 31.7 and 44.9",
                "mg/cm2 were used."
              ]
            }
          ],
